===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# [[widespread|Widespread]] [[disease]] that [[affect]]s many [[individual]]s in a [[population]]
# {{cattag|Epidemiology}} An [[occurrence]] of a disease or [[disorder]] in a population at a [[frequency]] higher than that expected in a given time period.

